{"tid":858292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"接受唔到自己鐘意咗個大陸男仔","createTime":"2018-10-11T16:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T17:57:52.000Z","uid":43783,"like":7,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"47410722599227add24e3bf809aed2de799978cb","tid":858292,"uid":43783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"做project冇得自己分組<br />\n同組有外國人 所以一向都用英文溝通<br />\n本身以為佢係local/abc 因為佢啲英文accent 好好聽<br />\n而佢俾我嘅第一印象係 好有氣質 好gentlemen <br />\n<br />\n有次坐正佢隔離 鼓起勇氣再撩佢傾計（英文）<br />\n結果傾足3個鐘 <br />\n然後有次直落食埋飯 <br />\n我屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢真係好有氣質 好幽默 同我有好多共同興趣<br />\n<br />\n每日起身就係期待佢send snapchat同我講gd morning <br />\n見到佢 我會變到好緊張 唔似平時咁從容<br />\n以前拍拖都未試過咁<br />\n我就發現我已經愛上咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到一次係campus 撞到佢同佢班frd <br />\n第一次親耳聽到佢講普通話 <br />\n真係好流利 就好似佢嘅母語咁<br />\n我諗 佢會唔會係台灣人呢<br />\n再一次 我見到佢用we7覆message <br />\n佢打嘅係我最憎嘅簡體字<br />\n我真係喊咗 我真係喊咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直以黎我都堅持男朋友要係香港人 本土意識要強<br />\n因為始終同聲同氣 有好多野 唔係香港人就唔會明<br />\n我諗過 可唔可以唔談政治 只談戀愛呢<br />\n應該唔會再遇到好似佢咁高質嘅香港男仔<br />\n但真係過唔到自己個關<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢係美國讀過書<br />\n但佢覺得香港係中國嘅<br />\n雖然佢知道中共唔好 <br />\n但佢始終會為佢嘅祖國自豪<br />\n佢係一個中國人 <br />\n<br />\n頭先收到佢message <br />\n一個我地好鐘意嘅鋼琴家黎香港開concert<br />\n佢約我一齊去睇<br />\n我打完呢篇文就會去覆佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可唔可以安慰下我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9071a3affd7c38adc1d590bf7ce54530274b8b0","tid":858292,"uid":4158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"佢條腸先安慰到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e39634d0809a7c477f9ead2657d7dab56674af","tid":858292,"uid":43783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c9071a3affd7c38adc1d590bf7ce54530274b8b0","tid":858292,"uid":4158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"佢條腸先安慰到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:40:57.000Z","msg":"唔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690d0bd7dc5f1f03f300f5f865cc5ab245803931","tid":858292,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200beed91e3e1cd19ddb7b46f8d6618939b3d941","tid":858292,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"cfad01c6264e1c2025e47b9d822d092b687f5cce","tid":858292,"uid":2795,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"gay佬生唔到下一代無咩所謂"},{"pid":"7b923fe64588e2caa7a2beb9f2f1b40e4766f72a","tid":858292,"uid":14083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"玩下好啦，我當年都食左好多大陸妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962211938003180ad8cec2659155471149a32d2a","tid":858292,"uid":5995,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"幫大陸仔含啦仆街"},{"pid":"3a827107b5690a289da0655cffdaefe993588665","tid":858292,"uid":43783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"962211938003180ad8cec2659155471149a32d2a","tid":858292,"uid":5995,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"幫大陸仔含啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔會再聯絡啦屌"},{"pid":"638af0f0aad2466bc879455f6650ad941a786904","tid":858292,"uid":183601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20